The paper discusses the failure modes of machine learning systems, which is a topic that falls under the categories of computer security (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), software engineering (cs.SE), and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, since the paper focuses on the security and safety aspects of machine learning systems, cs.CR and cs.LG are the most likely categories.
